# React frontend

Canonical structure: [front/sub.md](mdc:front/sub.md).

- React 19 + `react-scripts`; pages under `front/src/jsx/`; shared chrome in `front/src/components/layout/`
- Tailwind v3 (CRA): `tailwind.config.js`, `postcss.config.js`, `@tailwind` directives in `common.css`
- Shared CSS: `front/src/public/css/common.css` (import once in `index.js`)
- Page CSS: `front/src/public/css/<page>.css` (import in matching JSX)
- `App.js` wires the active screen (e.g. `Login`)
- Call backend at `http://localhost:3000` for `/api/*` in development

NEVER add a second global CSS file without updating `sub.md` and `AGENTS.md`.
